ygData.messageBody:
I don't know about now. Before the expansion came out, though,
KEdge Keep was packed on Solusek RO. SEveral times, my guild went
to go there, only to report "53 people in Kedge" and they'd
have to find something else to do.

>-----Original Message-----
>From: Rebecca Small [mailto:macha_nabaob@...]
>Sent: Tuesday, May 09, 2000 8:08 AM

>Hail Fellow Tunesmiths,
>
>Kinda anti climatic now, but Ding! Welcome to L50.
>All I can say is get a group together and start on the first floor
>of Kedge
>at L35 or so, and work your way through as you level up. The loot
>sucks, but
>the respawn rate makes this about the fastest experience place we
>have ever
>seen, and it's nearly always empty, even on Xegony.
>
>Lady Brilinnia Ban'Sidhe
>Knight Marshall, Order of the Rose
>Excalibur, Xegony
>
